OL,4,C'dangerous' dog attacks four people
OL,6,FDeanne McGinty from the CPS said:
OL,7,F"This was a frightening incident for
OL,8,Fmembers of the public, including
OL,9,Fchildren, who were holidaying at the
OL,10,Fpark and for the members of staff
OL,11,Fworking at the public house. The
OL,12,Fvictims have been left with permanent
OL,13,Fscars, a constant reminder of the
OL,14,Fincident. We hope the sentences passed
OL,15,Ftoday will bring some comfort to them".
OL,17,FLoftus was given a 14-month jail term,
OL,18,Fsuspended for 18 months, and must do
OL,19,F30 days of rehabilitation activity.
